g from the level - or flat - area between the bindings and the &apos;flat spot&apos; of Stage Three. Stage Two also acts as a secondary contact point when you are carving Standard Profile Poplar Core: thicker between the feet and tapers out as it reaches the nose and tail. There is no need for extra tapering as the nose and tail are already in the air because of the Rocker that starts at your feet Matte Nylon 8210 top for softer torsion flex Durasurf sintered base Triaxial glass top and bottom Carbon stringer tip to tail Length (cm): 148, 152, 154, 156, 158 Effective Edge (cm): 112 (148), 115 (152), 117 (154), 118 (156), 119 (158) Tip/Tail Width (cm): 27.8 (148), 28.6 (152), 29 (154), 29 (156), 29.3 (158) Waist Width (cm): 23.7 (148), 24.3 (152), 24.6 (154), 24.6 (156), 24.9 (158) Sidecut (m): 7.4 (148), 7.6 (152), 7.7 (154), 7.7 (156), 7.8 (158)', 'signal-rocker-snowboard-154.jpg', '389.00', '9.00', '1', '0', '2012-12-06 00:00:00', '2012-12-08 02:39:12'), ('717eac8d-4123-11e2-8c2b-f23c91934b7a', '50c33b07-341c-49d6-9856-08c2173e866a', 'Skate Shoes', '50c30e9b-a924-4162-86b7-0749173e866a', 'Habitat', 'Habitat Lark Mid In4Mation Skate Shoes Black/Gargoyle', 'habitat-lark-mid-in4mation-skate-shoes-black-gargoyle', '<br />Key Features of the Habitat Lark Mid In4Mation Skate Shoes: Traditional low profile skate silhouette Thin tongue and collar padding Seamless toecap Suede canvas and synthetic nubuck upper Recycled regrind/natural gum outsole Assembled with water-based glues Vulcanized outsole construction Premium PU footbed', 'habitat-lark-mid-in4mation-skate-shoes-black-gargoyle.jpg', '64.95', '6.00', '1', '0', '2012-12-06 00:00:00', '2012-12-08 02:39:12'), ('717eb08a-4123-11e2-8c2b-f23c91934b7a', '50c33b07-341c-49d6-9856-08c2173e866a', 'Snowboard Pants', '50c30ea1-d380-40d7-9c0c-0749173e866a', 'Sessions', 'Sessions Movement Snowboard Pants Black Magic', 'sessions-movement-snowboard-pants-black-magic', 'The Sessions Movement snowboard pants will keep you warm and dry