ion. <br />Key Features of the HO Pinnacle Combo Skis 67&quot; w/ Helix Std Bindings: Skill Level: Recreational Size Limit: 61&amp;#8221; Up to 150 lbs., 67&amp;#8221; Up to 200 lbs.', 'ho-pinnacle-combo-skis-67-quot-w-helix-std-bindings.jpg', '159.99', '6.00', '1', '0', '2012-12-06 00:00:00', '2012-12-08 02:39:37'), ('718159f1-4123-11e2-8c2b-f23c91934b7a', '50c33b07-341c-49d6-9856-08c2173e866a', 'Wakeboards', '50c30ea2-f634-4102-a268-0749173e866a', 'Slingshot', 'Slingshot Whip Wakeboard 139', 'slingshot-whip-wakeboard-139', 'Raising the bar again, Slingshot introduces the most versatile wakeboard ever. Taking the best attributes of our Ballistic Line, the 2012 Whip features enhanced molded channels and fins that increase its edging power, magnify its pop, and reduce its impact on hard landings. This all NEW board combines a rider friendly outline and continuous rocker with specific bottom features designed to make it fast, poppy, smooth on landings, and still hold up to the gnarliest torture riders can inflict. Whether you&amp;#8217;re shredding obstacles and boosting huge airs at your local cable park like Steffen Vollert or showing off behind your favorite boat, the 2012 Whip is sure to make it better.<br />Key Features of the Slingshot Whip Wakeboard: Intermediate &amp;#8211; Expert Like controlled and supportive traction on edg Want clean release on ollies and off the wake Looking for ultra efficient speed on and off edge Continuous Rocker: effortless pop and butter soft landings Future Response Technology&amp;#8482;: lighweight, more durable core that offers controlled flex that evenly distributes an explosive energy burst when popping off the wake and on ollies, and absorbs shock on hard landings Bio Sensor Core: simple wood core that offers a great feel, continuous momentum, controlled riding performance and stability in all conditions New Atomic C Core: a completely new core layout for this year. Its pure wood made of vertically laminated columbian gold, with custom molded channels Asymmetrical Molded Fins: added stability, increased hold on edge, and cleaner release off the wake V Bottom with Planning Rails: subtle convex belly increases agility and creates a landing sweet spot wihout decreasing momentum wiht side channels that direct momentum on flat landings and add stability on edges Adjustable Bolt On Fin Settings:two fin settings options (place fins in the outer setting for added edge hold and place fins in the inner setting for a looser feel and earlier release off the wake) Singleshot Fusion Sidewalls: high durometer urethane seamlessly fused into the core (The most durable and dampening wakeboard rail ever) NEW Slantwall: more impact resistant sidewalls with variable contoured sidecut to provide more grip up the wake with a clean release 4D Graphic Technology: the latest in graphic technology, giving every board individuality, and four dimensional depth Handmade by Slingshot in the USA: precision finished product using the highest quality materials', 'slingshot-whip-wakeboard-139.jpg', '398.95', '0.00', '1', '0', '2012-12-06 00:00:00', '2012-12-08 02:39:37'), ('71815da2-4123-11e2-8c2b-f23c91934b7a', '50c33b07-341c-49d6-9856-08c2173e866a', 'Towables', '50c30e9c-e4d4-4099-8d66-0749173e866a', 'HO', 'HO Hornet Towable Tube', 'ho-hornet-towable-tube', 'The Hornet is an HO classic! It is an incredible ride with its neoprene knuckle guards and soft foam filled handles. Its heavy duty PVC vinyl bladder and durable 420 denier nylon cover allow aggressive use! This is a great introduction to tubing!<br />Key Features of the HO Hornet Towable Tube: 54&amp;#8221; diameter (deflated) HO Quick Connect Tow Attachment Quick and Easy Inflation and Deflation Nylon Webbing Covered Soft Foam Handles Guaranteed Lasting Quality with our 1 Year Limited Warranty 2K Tube Rope Required', 'ho-hornet-towable-tube.jpg', '79.99', '2.00', '1', '0', '2012-12-06 00:00:00', '2012-12-08 02:39:37'), ('71816110-4123-11e2-8c2b-f23c91934b7a', '50c